Indicates whether the exception is the result of a failed access condition (ETag) check.

public static bool IsAccessConditionFailed (this Microsoft.Rest.Azure.CloudException exception);
Parameters
exception
Microsoft.Rest.Azure.CloudException

The exception to check.

Returns
Boolean

true if the exception is a failed access condition (HTTP 412 Precondition Failed), false otherwise.
